title: Ohio Rep. Brad Wenstrup on Eco Recovery

description:
Rep. Brad Wenstrup, a Republican representing Ohio's 2nd Congressional district discusses plans for the next economic stimulus package. He speaks with Bloomberg's Kevin Cirilli.
